/></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size:16px;\"><img src=\"{587.png}\" alt=\"\" /><br /></span></p>', 'admin', '2020-12-30 14:25:01', 'closed', '2021-01-06 11:09:44', '0000-00-00', '2020-12-28', 'admin', '2020-12-30 14:25:33', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'admin', '2021-01-06 11:09:44', 'done', 'admin', '2021-01-06 11:09:44', '0');
